snippet.title: I Am Setsuna – E3 2016 Trailer
snippet.description:
In a land of sorrow and bitter cold a tale of sacrifice will be told.
 
Experience the timeless story of I Am Setsuna.
 
Coming July 19th 2016 to PC and PSN
